0x9C7B59F9.name: GET_VEHICLE_WHEEL_WIDTH

params.name: vehicle
params.description: The vehicle to obtain data for.

0x9C7B59F9.description:
Returns vehicle's wheels' width (width is the same for all the wheels, cannot get/set specific wheel of vehicle).
Only works on non-default wheels (returns 0 in case of default wheels).
0x9C7B59F9.resultsDescription: Float representing width of the wheel (usually between 0.1 and 1.5)
